data.description: Home, sweet home! This charming 3-bedroom residence perfectly blends modern comfort and convenience. Displaying a 2-car garage and a front yard w/mature trees for a constant breeze. Enter to find a open layout paired with a neutral palette, archways, tons of natural light, and tasteful flooring - tile & plush carpet in all the right places. The kitchen comes with built-in appliances, a pantry, and ample wood cabinetry. Split bedroom floor pan for extra privacy! Primary bedroom has a private bathroom with a walk-in closet. Laundry room with attached cabinetry. Discover the backyard, an excellent spot for relaxing or entertaining! A covered patio, hot tub pad, storage shed, and fruit trees complete the picture. NO neighbors behind! Move-in ready!
